{"tid":965622,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"KAI愛Krystal、Jennie「冰山美人款」網：兩代女團門面都承包了！ 你地點揀？","createTime":"2019-01-02T07:55:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-05T04:34:56.000Z","uid":88491,"like":301,"dislike":34,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"9caad3cf53afef181fce40f1e77611081ba4069e","tid":965622,"uid":88491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T07:55:46.000Z","msg":"南韓媒體《Dispatch》每年1月1日都會爆出一對演藝圈情侶，2019年新春第一爆就相當震撼，EXO成員Kai與BLACKPINK成員Jennie被拍到深夜在公園約會，更被媒體目擊牽著彼此的手。Kai的前女友是他的青梅竹馬、同公司女團f(x)成員Krystal，和Jennie共通點都是「冰山美人」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/01/02/155154_423b6966c82e30c82b7142dcdaf27cfd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F01%2F02%2F155154_423b6966c82e30c82b7142dcdaf27cfd.png&h=448b44fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這已經不是Kai第一次被《Dispatch》曝光戀情，2016年愚人節當天被拍到與認識多年，從小就一起當練習生的同門女團f(x)成員Krystal秘戀，公司也大方認愛，被認證是「高顏值情侶」。不過因為行程繁忙，兩人在聚少離多的情況下，在2017年6月在公司證實下確定分手，回到同事關係。<br />\n<br />\n如今再爆出與BLACKPINK成員Jennie的戀愛消息，也不難看出Kai喜歡的類型，都是有著「冰山美人」氣質。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v1NfJ0Z.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv1NfJ0Z.png&h=e21df0bf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T01TvF2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT01TvF2.png&h=c7211af0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n如果你地係KAI 仔會點揀？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  Krystal <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Jennie</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"b631c4a379654964c1c631d1f570913381a12561","tid":965622,"uid":88491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T08:11:43.000Z","msg":"15:0 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56570f1e000845849d580d8bdeb3e50e47d3c055","tid":965622,"uid":7406